Package com.mhealthatlas.apps.dto

com.mhealthatlas.apps.dto contains all data transfer object definitions.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AndroidAppDetailInfoDto
    DTO for android application detail information.
    AndroidAppVersionDetailInfoDto
    DTO for android application version detail information.
    AppEventDto
    DTO for exchanging application and application version data via events.
    AppIdEventDto
    DTO for exchanging the application id via events.
    AppRelationEventDto
    DTO for exchanging application relationships via events.
    AppScoreEventDto
    DTO for exchanging the cusl score of an application version via events.
    AppVersionDto
    DTO for application version release date informations.
    AppVersionInfosDto
    DTO containing application version information and information about the returned data position in the database.
    AppVersionTaxonomyClassDto
    DTO containing the app version taxonomy class data.
    AppVersionTaxonomyClassEventDto
    DTO for exchanging a taxonomy class of an application version via events.
    IosAppDetailInfoDto
    DTO for ios application detail information.
    IosAppVersionDetailInfoDto
    DTO for ios application version detail information.
    MHealthAtlasAppDetailInfoDto
    DTO which wraps the AndroidAppDetailInfoDto and IosAppDetailInfoDto
    MHealthAtlasAppInfoDto
    DTO containing application version information
    MHealthAtlasAppInfosDto
    DTO containing application information and information about the returned data position in the database.
    MHealthAtlasAppShortInfoDto
    DTO containing only the most important application information
    MHealthAtlasAppShortInfosDto
    DTO containing application short information and information about the returned data position in the database.
    NewAndroidAppInfoDto
    DTO containing new android application and android application version informations.
    NewIosAppInfoDto
    DTO containing new ios application and ios application version informations.
    NewPrivateCustomerAppInfoDto
    DTO containing new private customer application and private customer application version informations.
    ScoreDto
    DTO for exchanging the cusl score of an application version taxonomy class.
    TaxonomyClassDto
    DTO for exchanging a taxonomy class via events.
    TaxonomyClassEventDto
    DTO for exchanging a taxonomy class via events.
